Package model

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Customer
  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    Represent a customer that consists of customer ID, its name, address, postal code, phone number, and division. Provides getters and setters for all the fields.
    Author:
    Iulia Bejsovec
